productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Eller has one of these. She works as a butler and she says it looks smoky.
This Dale, does exactly what it's suppose to do.
I tried to cremate it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
The box this comes in is 3 meter by 5 foot and weights 11 kilogram.
heard about this on folktronica radio, decided to give it a try.
